														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1792567">
									

<p>Author Commentary Time!</p>
<p>This was inspired by an article I read entitled &quot;I Hate Magic&quot;, which belittled how magic systems in several mediums were poorly represented, often being used to handwave attacks and abilities. This was my attempt to represent magic in the context of the Foundationverse, being studied by the Foundation. Of course, if they can't explain how it works, they won't use it in any practical context. Isn't that right, <a href="/scp-105">SCP-105</a>, <a href="/scp-076">SCP-076</a> and <a href="/scp-500">SCP-500</a>?</p>

							</div>

								
